description:

name: blossums through the snow
description:
Soft and pink, elegant and delicate, these beautiful earrings are reminiscent of the first blush of color through the snowy fields. Sleek ear wires give such a contemporary look to the classic pearl and, let me say, these button pearls are just so lustrous boasting 10mm in size. Divine. So easy to wear and sophisticated for day or night

The last picture illustrates earring length. They are my own personal earrings and only worn by me. Your purchase will be for a brand-new, unworn pair

P L E A S E • C H O O S E On check-out, just list your preference: Available in pink OR peacock black (also available in white in another listing)

T H E • D E T A I L
Measurements are over 1 1/2" (40mm) from top of earwire to pearl • Sterling silver earwires • Pink or peacock black freshwater pearl • Thai Village silver bead

name: this goes with that
description:
Introducing some fabulous earrings that are so cool with their wire ball mass. They simply go with everything (hence the obvious name!). Made by the Thai Karen Hill Tribe artisans, each cute ball is a work of art in themselves. Made from near solid silver wire (99% pure), a staple in every girl's earring collection

Earwire is handmade (by me!) using Thai Hill tribe silver wire

T H E • D E T A I L
Thai Hill tribe silver earwire and ball • 1 1/4" (30mm) drop from top of earwire to bottom of ball

name: amazonite queen
description:
This necklace makes such a bold statement mainly through its geometric shapes and subtlty rather than through any wild color. I just love the unusually cut gemstones with the tiny Hill Tribe silver beads adding interest within the stones

The milky light blue/green Amazonite is aply named from the Amazon River in Brazil which is one of the locations where it is found, and it is said that it carries the qualities of the strong female warrior! Bearing that in mind, I had better do them justice with adding other special stunners - Turquoise and dark green Jasper

Very comfortable to wear sitting easily on the collarbone and with its pastel hues is easy to wear with almost anything

T H E • D E T A I L
Measurements are 22"/56cm from end to end • 3 Amazonite gemstones are 1.5"/40mm x 1"/25mm and 6 Turquoise and 4 Japser beads
